* all integrals and volumes are taken with respect to the Haar measure on formula_21 or its quotients. 

The left-hand side of the formula is called the &quot;geometric side&quot; and the right-hand side the &quot;spectral side&quot;. The terms formula_29 are orbital integrals. 

