*James Burnett to T. Cadell and J. Davies, 15 May 1796, British Museum, A letter bound into Dugald Stewart, &quot;Account of the Life and Writings of William Robertson, D.D., F.R.S.E&quot;, 2nd ed., London (1802). Shelf no.1203.f.3

